Create Victims Per Shooting by Shooters' Age Group 15

Step 1. Copy and paste the Victims Per Shooting by Month visual

Step 2. Remove all the Date Hierarchy  from the Shared Axis well.

Step 3. Drag and Drop Age Group to the Shared Axis well and follow the                  steps in the Gif.


Step 8. Turn the visual shadow on


Steps

In this step we will turn the visual shadow on to make it standout against the background.

  1. Click on the Visual.
  2. Go to Format Pane and turn the shadow on as shown in the image above.
